OL,3,CBen Stokes' house 'burgled by masked
OL,4,Cgang while family were inside'
OL,6,FBen Stokes has said a masked gang
OL,7,Fburgled his home while his wife and
OL,8,Fchildren were inside and he was on
OL,9,FEngland duty.
OL,11,FThe Durham cricketer said his family
OL,12,Fdid not come to "any physical harm" in
OL,13,Fthe incident at his home in the Castle
OL,14,FEden area of County Durham but several
OL,15,F"irreplaceable and sentimental" items
OL,16,Fwere taken.
OL,18,FThe England test captain was in
OL,19,FPakistan for the recent test match at
OL,20,Fthe time of the burglary on the
OL,21,Fevening of Thursday 17 October.
