OL,6,FIn an appeal on social media, Stokes
OL,7,Fasked for help to find the items which
OL,8,Fhe said were stolen including
OL,9,Fjewellery, handbags and the OBE medal
OL,10,Fhe received in 2020.
OL,12,FHe also shared pictures of a number of
OL,13,Fthe missing items and thanked Durham
OL,14,FConstabulary for their "outstanding
OL,15,Fsupport" since the incident.
OL,17,FWriting on X, he said: "On the evening
OL,18,Fof Thursday 17th October a number of
OL,19,Fmasked people burgled my home in the
OL,20,FCastle Eden area in the North East.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
