OL,3,CBen Stokes' house 'burgled by masked
OL,4,Cgang while family were inside'
OL,6,F"They escaped with jewellery, other
OL,7,Fvaluables and a good deal of personal
OL,8,Fitems. Many of those items have real
OL,9,Fsentimental value for me and my
OL,10,Ffamily. They are irreplaceable.
OL,12,F"This is an appeal for any help in
OL,13,Ffinding the people who carried out
OL,14,Fthis act.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
