OL,3,CBen Stokes' house 'burgled by masked
OL,4,Cgang while family were inside'
OL,6,F"By far the worst thing about this
OL,7,Fcrime is that it was carried out
OL,8,Fwhilst my wife and 2 young children
OL,9,Fwere in the house. Thankfully, none of
OL,10,Fmy family came to any physical harm.
OL,11,FUnderstandably, however, the
OL,12,Fexperience has had an impact on their
OL,13,Femotional and mental state. All we can
OL,14,Fthink about is how much worse this
OL,15,Fsituation could have been.
OL,17,F"I am releasing photographs of some of
OL,18,Fthe stolen items - which I hope may be
OL,19,Feasily identified - in the hope that
OL,20,Fwe can find the people who are
OL,21,Fresponsible for this.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
