OL,3,CBen Stokes' house 'burgled by masked
OL,4,Cgang while family were inside'
OL,6,F"Although we have lost cherished
OL,7,Fpossessions, to be clear, my sole
OL,8,Fmotivation in sharing these
OL,9,Fphotographs is not the recovery of
OL,10,Fmaterial items. It is to catch the
OL,11,Fpeople who did this.
OL,13,F"Finally, I want to say thank you to
OL,14,Fthe police service. Both now and
OL,15,Fwhilst I was away in Pakistan, their
OL,16,Fsupport for my family has been
OL,17,Foutstanding. They continue to work
OL,18,Fincredibly hard in trying to find
OL,19,Fthese people."
